      "name": "Retreat",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "gm": "",
          "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisite</strong> Your army is not @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.kingmaker-features.Item.2IqM1XHELKwARAx1]{Engaged}.</p>\n<p>Your army tries to escape from the battlefield.</p>\n<p>If your army is already @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.kingmaker-features.Item.8upne4E6Q7Da5T5w]{Distant}, it flees the battlefield, is no longer part of the war encounter, and becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.kingmaker-features.Item.aZImSBBmTHff2POP]{Routed}. </p>\n<p>Otherwise, your army gains the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.kingmaker-features.Item.8upne4E6Q7Da5T5w]{Distant} condition.</p>"
        },
