      "system": {
        "description": {
          "gm": "",
          "value": "<p>The army's ranged attacks explode and spray fire, shrapnel, or other damaging material in every direction. Whenever the army critically hits a non-distant army with a ranged Strike, inflict 1 point of additional damage to another non-distant enemy army of your choice. You can use the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.kingmaker-features.Item.HLu1o1RzCZxWjOJJ]{Overwhelming Bombardment} tactical war action with the army.</p>"
